spec_data.Name: python-mozrunner
spec_data.Description:
Mozrunner is a Python package which handles running of Mozilla
applications.  Mozrunner utilizes mozprofile for managing application
profiles and mozprocess for robust process control.  Mozrunner may be
used from the command line or programmatically as an API.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 02:06:30 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Reliable start/stop/configuration of Mozilla Applications (Firefox, Thunderbird)
